	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<note>[Anfang fehlt, ist abgeschnitten].</note>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">An in armis sit <persName type="auto_name">Navarrus</persName>, non facile dixero; nam post literas illas nihil praeterea accepi necdum audio, communicarem alioqui.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad d. <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvinum</persName> scribam, ut mones, successum permissurus deo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pecunias illas depositas esse <placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolani</placeName>, consulibus indicavi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Horum alter dicit se recessum misisse d. consuli vestro.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Ex <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Clarona</placeName> haec hodie accepi:</foreign> Verganges frytags ist zuͦ <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Glarus</placeName> ein lantman toub worden, hat sin spieß genommen, ist gen <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l458">Schwanden</placeName> umb die 2 gägen tag geloffen, geschruwen: mordio, figendio.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Deß ist ein glöuff worden, das in einer stund ein hüpsch volck by einandren xin; doch wie sy vernommen.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">wie der mensch toub, hat man inn gefangen gen <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Glarus</placeName> gefürt, in ysen glegt, und wie er da hüpschlich gethan, das man imm vertruwt, hat er 3 eerenmann, under denen ouch der aman <persName type="auto_name">Hässig</persName> einer ist, verwundet etc.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta Vindelicorum</placeName> habeo semina belli sparsa esse et spargi; nam <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916" cert="high">Sebastianum Schertlinum</persName> in controversiam venisse cum <persName type="auto_name">Ludovico</persName>, comite <placeName type="auto_name">Oetingensi</placeName>, propter ius nescio quod venandi etc.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habet uterque suos, qui instigent.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Prudentes colligunt nescio quid.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex urbe <placeName ref="l522" cert="high">Venetorum</placeName> scribitur <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510">Turcam</placeName> duci <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1098" cert="high">Florentino</placeName> ex portu abduxisse triremes 3 et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcae</placeName> metum esse magnum in <placeName ref="l834" type="auto_name">Italia</placeName>; parare itaque se papam, <placeName type="auto_name">Florentinum</placeName>, <placeName type="auto_name">Sabaudum</placeName>, <persName type="citizen_name">Philippum</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hispanum</placeName> etc., quod appetente vere expectent Turcicam classem certo venturam contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834">Italiam</placeName> et maxime <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2556" cert="high">Siciliam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Vilicht wirt das frid uff nemmen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus det nobis pacem etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vive et vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 15. novembris 1560.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant te nostri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutato optimos viros d. d. consules, <persName type="auto_name">Philippum</persName>, <persName ref="p6130" cert="high">Pontasellam</persName> et alios amicos.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">[Pre]stantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioan[ni] Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> [eccl]esiae ministro fide[li], domino et compatri [m]eo colendo et percharo.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gen <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName> dem pfarrer zuͦ S. Martin.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
